{"tid":395863,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"監警會上半年776宗投訴 指控包括警毆打恐嚇換認罪","createTime":"2017-09-11T07:39:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-11T14:12:56.000Z","uid":75969,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"78b46b1a728920821f2f6de0d437060878e1f731","tid":395863,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T07:39:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170911/small/1505107388_d255.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170911%2Fsmall%2F1505107388_d255.jpg&h=4df60c58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n監警會指，今年上半年合共通過776宗投訴個案，其中213宗屬有關刑事調查衍生的投訴，不少關於投訴人指控警員，以毆打、誘導或恐嚇等不當手段取得投訴人的招認，或指警方所記錄的供詞不正確等。<br />\n<br />\n主席郭琳廣稱，該213宗個案中，有47宗需經投訴警察課全面調查並由監警會審核，當中39宗被分類為虛假不確或並無過錯、8宗無法證實。其餘166宗個案為無法追查或撤回投訴。他說，部份個案的投訴人，當初很可能是基於抗辯需要才投訴有關警員，屬策略性投訴。<br />\n<br />\n另外，今年共有44宗投訴個案成立，當中8宗與刑事調查有關。副秘書長梅達明指，該8宗個案牽涉認人手續的記錄欠妥當、起訴嫌疑人較輕的控罪及有足夠情況下仍釋放疑犯等。他說，目前未見有特別的投訴趨勢，強調監警會處理投訴會不偏不倚。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170911/57195250\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170911%2F57195250&d=zm1YLSEXK%2Bh7fiA9yBSUQROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=92a3b0dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170911%2F57195250&h=8c0421be\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170911/57195250</a>"},{"pid":"a85a66fb5b783b81b916c82b829f54962a1f91f2","tid":395863,"uid":3117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T07:51:31.000Z","msg":"根本同呂樂時代反貪污部一撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6d63b7c8a69d139dde1722dacb5e153fcce4a61","tid":395863,"uid":10064,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T07:52:20.000Z","msg":"報都776<br />\n冇報個d...."},{"pid":"0fd5060c55d6d5606538fa9dae84fcc0fac6dec1","tid":3958